About J.A.R.V.I.S.

J.A.R.V.I.S. (Just A Rather Very Intelligent System) is an AI-powered personal assistant designed to help you with various tasks, from answering questions to managing your schedule. Built with cutting-edge technology and a focus on user experience, J.A.R.V.I.S. aims to make your digital life more efficient and enjoyable.

Features

  • Natural Language Processing
  • Task Management
  • Information Retrieval
  • Personalized Responses
  • Multi-platform Support

Tech Stack

  • React & Material-UI
  • Node.js & Express
  • Python & FastAPI
  • MongoDB
  • OpenAI API
